WEBVTT

00:00.934 --> 00:02.641
NARRATOR:
In the criminal justice system

00:02.703 --> 00:06.617
the people are represented by two
separate yet equally important groups,

00:06.673 --> 00:08.482
the police
who investigate crime

00:08.542 --> 00:11.318
and the district attorneys
who prosecute the offenders.

00:11.378 --> 00:13.119
These are their stories.

00:14.848 --> 00:16.691
LUISA: Tena,
Daddy's waiting for us.

00:17.117 --> 00:18.790
I'm waving to Max.

00:19.553 --> 00:22.898
Put on your coat and your gloves.
I won't tell you twice.

00:23.724 --> 00:25.203
And bring me Elena's hat.

00:30.797 --> 00:31.901
Can I bring Lily?

00:31.965 --> 00:33.035
Yes, but hurry.

00:33.133 --> 00:34.840
(SPEAKING SPANISH)

00:39.139 --> 00:40.482
I don't see Daddy and Max.

00:40.541 --> 00:41.849
Leon?

00:45.612 --> 00:47.023
Leon!

00:47.381 --> 00:49.054
(SPEAKING SPANISH)

00:52.786 --> 00:55.426
Max! Max!

01:00.594 --> 01:02.164
(SCREAMING IN SPANISH)

01:02.896 --> 01:05.399
The 5-year-old died
en-route to North General.

01:05.799 --> 01:08.211
Mr. Galvez was
dead at the scene.

01:08.268 --> 01:09.576
CURTIS: What were they
doing out this early?

01:09.670 --> 01:11.343
They were going to their
grandmother's in Albany.

01:11.405 --> 01:14.818
Point of impact was here, knocked
the kid right out of his boots.

01:15.142 --> 01:16.553
BRISCOE: You got a make on
the hit-and-run?

01:16.610 --> 01:17.953
NORRIS: No.
No witnesses so far.

01:18.445 --> 01:19.480
Want to see the other one?

01:19.546 --> 01:20.547
Other one?

01:20.614 --> 01:22.093
Around the corner.

01:22.482 --> 01:23.517
CURTIS: Any ID?

01:23.584 --> 01:25.359
NORRIS: Be my guest.

01:25.419 --> 01:28.263
I'll wager he didn't
live in Harlem.

01:29.890 --> 01:32.962
Peter Lavalle,
170 East 82nd Street.

01:33.026 --> 01:35.006
Long way from his townhouse.

01:35.062 --> 01:37.269
We're positing he got
hit at the crosswalk.

01:37.831 --> 01:40.869
The car swerved
after the impact,

01:40.934 --> 01:43.312
hit the curb going
around the corner,

01:44.137 --> 01:47.812
we got tire marks there,
then hit the other two.

01:48.008 --> 01:49.919
Anybody hear him
hit the brakes?

01:49.977 --> 01:51.820
No brakes.
No skid marks.

01:52.613 --> 01:54.286
Maybe no accident.

